{"tid":1694380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"哈維·丹特呼籲葛咸城市民與蝙蝠俠割蓆","createTime":"2019-11-05T06:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T14:25:58.000Z","uid":67454,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c6939e76ff27ab2a584ec73fa8c1da0a632ea0ca","tid":1694380,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:34:53.000Z","msg":"前葛咸城檢察官、現任葛咸城犯罪聯盟主席哈維&middot;丹特認為，昨日小丑與葛咸城警局就衝突上的問題根源是蝙蝠俠的「暴力」，「私了停止咗落嚟，小丑唔洗回應，大家幾好呢，戈登局長又唔洗咁辛苦，可以正常咁射波，就唔洗捉一啲咁樣&hellip;&hellip;啲人亦跑得好辛苦，大家都。」<br />\n<br />\n有記者續追問指葛咸城罪犯針對平民已成常態，是否應有系統性調查解決。哈維則指，聯盟設有稻草人帶領的和諧部隊，在現場擔任調解員，「我相信呢啲係人同人既工程，一定可以透過大家既關係和態度既改變，能夠靠恐懼毒氣紓緩個氣氛。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d7e350c24d2178adea8f4a58a87bbda1866373","tid":1694380,"uid":74163,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:37:20.000Z","msg":"高登局長呢"},{"pid":"d556e26fe830b0edda6d4bc0b39b4ac5cf7325fe","tid":1694380,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48d7e350c24d2178adea8f4a58a87bbda1866373","tid":1694380,"uid":74163,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:37:20.000Z","msg":"高登局長呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:41:59.000Z","msg":"局長=和理非"},{"pid":"2f7a61c8485b638fc2eb9310c2cfbc48160371f5","tid":1694380,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d556e26fe830b0edda6d4bc0b39b4ac5cf7325fe","tid":1694380,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48d7e350c24d2178adea8f4a58a87bbda1866373","tid":1694380,"uid":74163,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:37:20.000Z","msg":"高登局長呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:41:59.000Z","msg":"局長=和理非"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:53:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班恩呢"},{"pid":"52793ee5d480b7e9249201940ac270aed6b00c2b","tid":1694380,"uid":35348,"like":